Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.42,0:00:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迈凯伦加入Extreme E因为最初我们认为这是一项很不错的赛事
Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.42,0:00:05.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}McLaren's entering Extreme E because first we think it's a fascinating championship.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:05.60,0:00:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们在开拓创新领域有很悠久的历史
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.60,0:00:08.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have a long history in pioneering and innovation,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:08.80,0:00:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这显然也是Extreme E系列赛的基础
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.80,0:00:12.67,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}which is clearly what the Extreme E championship has been founded on
Dialogue: 2,0:00:12.67,0:00:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可持续发展和多样性，这是当今世界面临的两大问题
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.67,0:00:17.55,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and sustainability and diversity, two very important issues in the world today
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.55,0:00:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们认为我们可以利用赛车这个平台展示我们的实力
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.55,0:00:21.47,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and we feel we can use the racing platform to put on a great show,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.47,0:00:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}同时也促进我们对可持续发展的认知
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.47,0:00:24.77,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}but also to accelerate our learning in sustainability
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.77,0:00:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从而使这个世界变得更加美好
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.77,0:00:27.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and being able to contribute to making the world a better place.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.97,0:00:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迈凯伦基本就是赛车运动
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.97,0:00:31.35,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}McLaren is basically motorsport.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.35,0:00:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迈凯伦是赛车的历史
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.35,0:00:33.37,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}McLaren is the history of motorsport.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:33.37,0:00:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迈凯伦是荣耀与光辉
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.37,0:00:34.57,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}McLaren is the glory.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迈凯伦在许多系列赛中都斩获过冠军
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.25,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}McLaren is the titles in many different championships.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.25,0:00:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}同时我们也能从迈凯伦看到未来
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.25,0:00:40.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And then also McLaren is the view of the future.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.55,0:00:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迈凯伦代表着我们希望纳入Extreme E的元素：
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.55,0:00:45.25,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And McLaren represents really what we want to have in Extreme E:
Dialogue: 2,0:00:45.25,0:00:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一个伟大的竞争者、一支能争冠的车队
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.25,0:00:47.85,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}a great competitor, a team that is a winner
Dialogue: 2,0:00:47.85,0:00:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}同时也是一支车队能和我们一样重视保护我们的地球、保护环境
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.85,0:00:54.37,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}but also a team that shares our values for the preservation of our planet, of the environment.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:54.37,0:00:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我认为这会给Extreme E增光添彩
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.37,0:00:56.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think it's a great addition to Extreme E.
